  <h3 class=" unit-title">What is it?</h3><br>
  <p>Risk: World War 1 is a total conversion mod for Starcraft 2. The map consists of Europe and Northern Africa, and players start by choosing one of 9 possible nations. The first team is the Entente (sometimes called the Allies) and consists of France, Russia, Britain, Italy, and Serbia. The second team is the Central Powers, and consists of Germany, Austria-Hungary, Bulgaria, and the Ottoman Empire. There are also neutral nations, which cannot be player controlled, and will always defend themselves when attacked.</p>
